tion introduces several novel elements to the field:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Integration of a recommendation system for method selection based on user requirements&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Evaluation of embedding quality using advanced metrics (NMSE, PSNR)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;A comprehensive framework for future steganography implementations&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Educational modules with interactive elements and pseudocode examples&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;The project successfully bridges the gap between theoretical knowledge and practical application in steganography, making complex concepts accessible to students, researchers, and cybersecurity professionals.&lt;/p&gt;&quot;
